      <p>In the European Union, only the most exclusive high quality crystal can have a round golden sticker on it. Lower quality crystal can only use square and triangular stickers. All of BrenndeL's crystal items are certified "Exclusive Quality" and have a round golden sticker on the foot of the item.</p>
